{"tid":97022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【未來特首候選人喎】林鄭速磅$500予支那來港行乞婦","createTime":"2017-01-27T10:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T15:03:57.000Z","uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"33267df675e928f911d08ac530efcf90c15c0394","tid":97022,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:42:18.000Z","msg":"【特首選戰】林鄭速磅$500予支那來港行乞婦：你辛苦嘞 新年好！<br />\n<br />\n【新增林鄭見記者】獲西環熱捧的特首參選人林鄭月娥，下午到沙田探基層，爭取民意，當她由小瀝源一直走到沙田政府合署的排頭村，看見有婆婆在街邊行乞，林鄭問婆婆有沒有住家、是不是香港人，婆婆擰頭否認，林鄭即「轉channel」、用普通話與婆婆交談幾句，再給婆婆一張$500港幣，並說「你辛苦嘞」、「新年好！小心一點兒」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭再會見傳媒時，回應標時問題，表示她正參選特首，最重要是聆聽和溝通，而香港還有很多事情要解決，勞工權益是其中一項，所以未來會多與各界探討，收窄分歧，在和諧社會氣氛下，解決長期困擾的問題。<br />\n<br />\n她續指，在政府工作36年多，明白問題複雜，不過「我一向以嚟都有一種迎難而上嘅精神」，過去亦解決過棘手的問題，冀往後能本著迎難而上的精神繼續努力。她又強調，不具體回應標時問題，不是因擔心失去某一方的支持與否，而是競選期間要多聽意見，加上她非現任官員，不宜評論現時政策。<br />\n<br />\n對於她被曾任政務司司長和財政司司長的唐英年形容欠缺經濟經驗，林鄭說「唔緊要嘅，任何人對我有咩嘅評價，我都係好謙虛咁去接受大家大嘅意見」，又指在沙田區，很感受到居民認同她的工作，令她很受鼓勵，相反若有人認為不足，她會很努力地學習，「事實上我喺每一個工作崗位都係先學習、聆聽、溝通，然後我就付諸行動，因為我都係一個行動型嘅人」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170127&amp;guid=56231882&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170127%26guid%3D56231882%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=hlyny7b2ObwFXf74lG9jsHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=0df25e2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170127%26guid%3D56231882%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=d312e247\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170127&amp;guid=56231882&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"4bca70ea713d8cdb8c075c0f9cdf08404b0428bf","tid":97022,"uid":79519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38eb03a2f65cf1fd5f19417dda9ab1673f3a707f","tid":97022,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"集團式都比5舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82010fe622b8abfc34d2204fe707980dab33a7a","tid":97022,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:47:58.000Z","msg":"淋病當選特首後！<br />\n<br />\n以後入境處同黑警都唔洗做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n非法行乞兼違反逗留條件，都可以得關愛基金每日派五百蚊。"},{"pid":"eabcd8e174d937d475d00c399b09d85879753ed5","tid":97022,"uid":13614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:47:58.000Z","msg":"佢做到會將大把港紙送比大陸乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7e57d53a6187838b3bacad8926724aadcdf551","tid":97022,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:50:16.000Z","msg":"支持犯罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac5ee61da11e665e6f175ff572923bdf78f2725","tid":97022,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:50:16.000Z","msg":"根據《簡易程序治罪條例》（第228章）第26A條，任何人士在公眾地方、街道或水道乞取或收取施捨，均屬犯罪，定罪後可被處罰款500元及監禁（第一或第二次定罪為一個月，而第三次或其後定罪則為12個月）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201602/03/P201602030394.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201602%2F03%2FP201602030394.htm&d=hlyny7b2ObwFXf74lG9jsHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5ca59f04\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201602/03/P201602030394.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭唔知行乞犯法?"},{"pid":"0f01e52e7d383a3b7f5a4d581c6c13fe5f5d71a7","tid":97022,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根據《簡易程序治罪條例》（第228章）第26A條，任何人士在公眾地方、街道或水道乞取或收取施捨，均屬犯罪，定罪後可被處罰款500元及監禁（第一或第二次定罪為一個月，而第三次或其後定罪則為12個月）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201602/03/P201602030394.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201602%2F03%2FP201602030394.htm&d=hlyny7b2ObwFXf74lG9jsHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5ca59f04\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201602/03/P201602030394.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭唔知行乞犯法?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記住數先，唔係佢上台就要報驚"},{"pid":"c8789d6b5f7ade15e9eb7c929bfdf46de0012480","tid":97022,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:52:18.000Z","msg":"高分低能嘛係呢d，又柒出國際"},{"pid":"a1a3fc331a93e55a0d9c60be55ea1ac274f74626","tid":97022,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:52:23.000Z","msg":"淋病新政網：<br />\n<br />\n為鼓勵自由行旅客在香港非法行乞及違反逗留條件，關愛基金將會每天派發五百元，予行乞的中國內地公民。"},{"pid":"917bc0b58bf668c6d87b27581c9e775605617ae4","tid":97022,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淋病當選特首後！<br />\n<br />\n以後入境處同黑警都唔洗做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n非法行乞兼違反逗留條件，都可以得關愛基金每日派五百蚊。</blockquote><br />\n呢個八婆柒到幾時先停呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b700daef1211ce4f8b3582b54e2ab9efe740421","tid":97022,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淋病當選特首後！<br />\n<br />\n以後入境處同黑警都唔洗做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n非法行乞兼違反逗留條件，都可以得關愛基金每日派五百蚊。</blockquote><br />\n呢個八婆柒到幾時先停呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n豬過唐英年。。。。"},{"pid":"175681d240afd34926f8b03f397f350a9aca1e26","tid":97022,"uid":79919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:55:22.000Z","msg":"10億 乘 500。等如幾多呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea1c55e6cb8b75e1968d869eddafac12432ff1d","tid":97022,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:55:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>根據《簡易程序治罪條例》（第228章）第26A條，任何人士在公眾地方、街道或水道乞取或收取施捨，均屬犯罪，定罪後可被處罰款500元及監禁（第一或第二次定罪為一個月，而第三次或其後定罪則為12個月）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201602/03/P201602030394.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201602%2F03%2FP201602030394.htm&d=hlyny7b2ObwFXf74lG9jsHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5ca59f04\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201602/03/P201602030394.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭唔知行乞犯法?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記住數先，唔係佢上台就要報驚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n林鄭特別幫佢比果500蚊入獄費，等佢可以免費食一個月皇家飯。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大慈善家"},{"pid":"939be2e4f54e0d46db09608ef4aff167a2338025","tid":97022,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"大家組團去搵佢，講普通話，一人五舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10eeb2dab84813c1b4aabed32c382c2486b5e4d4","tid":97022,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:57:23.000Z","msg":"比知對方犯緊法<br />\n<br />\n仲要比錢對方洗<br />\n<br />\n呢D人竟然係政府做左三十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64eec24b48959b06541c87e459d346f9e0582314","tid":97022,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家組團去搵佢，講普通話，一人五舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n五舊多過去幫鳩溶同靜心BB 做嘢。"},{"pid":"a3bb6ad858af93a6258d1f2fa9ce0a7147a27ae7","tid":97022,"uid":34037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ac8fae44a86a1c56173c4390f1f9b13fb16fa5","tid":97022,"uid":54951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:00:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比知對方犯緊法<br />\n<br />\n仲要比錢對方洗<br />\n<br />\n呢D人竟然係政府做左三十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以為自己做緊親民形象，都幾撚豬下"},{"pid":"6368c460dd7c8e3b251076b021a7fcafb88f6c37","tid":97022,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">明</span>知對方犯緊法<br />\n<br />\n仲要比錢對方洗<br />\n<br />\n呢D人竟然係政府做左三十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9eeb417705fd45731bd7899825162125da5a58dd","tid":97022,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>根據《簡易程序治罪條例》（第228章）第26A條，任何人士在公眾地方、街道或水道乞取或收取施捨，均屬犯罪，定罪後可被處罰款500元及監禁（第一或第二次定罪為一個月，而第三次或其後定罪則為12個月）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201602/03/P201602030394.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201602%2F03%2FP201602030394.htm&d=hlyny7b2ObwFXf74lG9jsHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5ca59f04\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201602/03/P201602030394.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭唔知行乞犯法?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記住數先，唔係佢上台就要報驚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n林鄭特別幫佢比果500蚊入獄費，等佢可以免費食一個月皇家飯。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大慈善家</blockquote><br />\n林鄭:我晌政府做三十幾年, 我知道點樣係唔犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6eeaa967a300c8394a765b136349d651c79732","tid":97022,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:03:06.000Z","msg":"公然鼓吹犯法"},{"pid":"e4c61940a9daea8e83f3e4700967b5b687bf69e4","tid":97022,"uid":6638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:03:20.000Z","msg":"強烈支持所有乞衣搵林鄭開飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71df2ebfd77db28a99f75a72ab92b67f89f78058","tid":97022,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:03:54.00